data.description: Welcome home to your private oasis, sitting on just over one acre,  yet still close to downtown conveniences!  With over 1,600 square feet, there is space for everyone in this ranch home, including a large living room, sunken family room, 3 spacious bedrooms, and two full bathrooms.  The first floor laundry is centrally located for convenience, and the raised ceiling in the large kitchen provide the perfect rustic feel!  Outside you have a large 24x40 heated garage, complete with a workshop and half bathroom on the main level, and a spacious studio apartment, including kitchenette and full bathroom upstairs.  Would make the perfect place for out of town family and friends to stay, or even and AirBnB!  Sit on your large back deck over looking abundant wildlife in your large yard, which also has mature trees, a fenced in garden area and 2 storage sheds.  The possibilities are endless!
